name: Deliver The Senbo
description:
Videogame made for the twitch streamer Enviosity (twitch.tv/enviosity sub with twitch prime btw).

If experiencing framerate issues, bugs and weird visuals, try with the downloadable version.

Play as their OC and deliver the Senbo plushies he just launched to their houses as fast as possible while jumping, dashing and boosting yourself through the levels in this extremely short platformer, but avoid all the pepegas, dinkdonks and omegaluls, as well as the covid virus if you want to make it alive!

Made with Unity.
